#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/tbl.md:216
msgid "`ptool.tbl.reduce(list, initial, fn)` folds a list into a single value."
msgstr "`ptool.tbl.reduce(list, initial, fn)` reduz uma lista a um único valor."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/versioned_docs/version-0.10.0/lua-api/tbl.md:218
